title: No new cases of Ebola reported for first time since March 2014 – UN health ...
text: ( Source : UN - United Nations ) 8 October 2015 - There were no new cases of Ebola reported in West Africa in the week ending last Sunday, making it the first week since March 2014 with zero cases recorded in the three countries most affected
